  "title": "ZiiM-Hud",
  "description": "A nice simple modular hud to display useful information.",
  "body": "<p>&nbsp;<br /><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Requirements:</strong></span></p>\n<p>This mod requires fabric API and mod menu<br /><br /><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" width=\"188\" height=\"63\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Features:</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>Fully moveable and customizable</b></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shows your current biome</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shows your current&nbsp;position</span><u><br /></u></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shows your current position in the nether</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shows your current direction</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shows your current effects</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shows your XP percentage</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shows your armor and armor durability</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shows the server IP</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shows your ping</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shows your local time</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shows your current FPS</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br /><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Commands:</strong></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">,textcolor [module] [r] [g] [b]<br />,datacolor [module] [r] [g] [b]<br /></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Keybinds:</strong></span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">p - Open editing screen. Allowing you to drag modules around</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">middle-click- Middle clicking while in editing screen disables/enables modules.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Modules:</strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">fps</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">tps</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">ping</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">biome</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">direction</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">pos</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">netherpos</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">time</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">xp</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">ip</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Pictures:</h2>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XH8etpz.gif\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DRM4U9Y.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
